          "reviewBody": "If you are looking for a school which gives 360 degrees development for your child, then Vedh Valley World School is the choice. It has a curriculum which teaches academic and non-academic subjects equally. My daughter has been studying here since last 4 years and there is not a single day that she would miss school. The development that I have seen in her is remarkable.\nThe school is very well staffed with very talented, hard working and  sincere\nteachers and Admin staff and a very very dedicated Principal, Chetana Madam. The efforts that the school puts into the students is visible to all. The students of VVWS  will excel in all fields of Life. This teachers Day, I wish all the dedicated teachers of Vedh Valley a very very Happy Teachers Day.",
